thread.title: BRIEF-Tessi H1 operating income rises to 22.1 million euros
thread.title_full: BRIEF-Tessi H1 operating income rises to 22.1 million euros | Reuters

author: Reuters
title: BRIEF-Tessi H1 operating income rises to 22.1 million euros
text:
Sept 3 Tessi SA :
* H1 operating income 22.1 million euros ($24.5 million) versus 16.4 million euros a year ago
* H1 net income group share 13.0 million euros versus 9.7 million euros a year ago
Source text: bit.ly/1EDCX5O Further company coverage: ($1 = 0.9008 euros) (Gdynia Newsroom)
